    "ts": pd.to_datetime([

```python
df_merged = df_event.merge(df_user, how='left', on='user_id')
display(df_merged)
df_merged_sorted = df_merged.sort_values(by=['user_id', 'ts'], ascending=[True, True])
df_merged_sorted['delta_min'] = (
    df_merged_sorted['ts'] - df_merged_sorted.groupby('user_id')['ts'].shift(1)
).dt.total_seconds() / 60
df_merged_sorted['is_new_session'] =  df_merged_sorted['delta_min'] > pd.Timedelta(minutes=30)
df_merged_sorted['session_id']=df_merged_sorted.groupby('user_id')['is_new_session'].cumsum()
display(df_merged_sorted)
import numpy as np
df_merged_sorted['is_view']     = df_merged_sorted['event'].eq('view')
df_merged_sorted['is_cart']     = df_merged_sorted['event'].eq('add_to_cart')
df_merged_sorted['is_purchase'] = df_merged_sorted['event'].eq('purchase')

df_merged_sorted['purchase_amt'] = np.where(
    df_merged_sorted['is_purchase'],
    df_merged_sorted['amount'],
    0
)
session_feat = (
    df_merged_sorted
    .groupby(['user_id', 'session_id', 'channel'], as_index=False)
    .agg(
        has_view     = ('is_view', 'any'),
        has_cart     = ('is_cart', 'any'),
        has_purchase = ('is_purchase', 'any'),
        revenue      = ('purchase_amt', 'sum')
    )
)
display(session_feat)
channel_funnel = session_feat.groupby('channel').agg(
    sessions = ('session_id', 'count'),
    view_sessions = ('has_view', 'sum'),
    cart_sessions = ('has_cart', 'sum'),
    purchase_sessions = ('has_purchase', 'sum'),
).reset_index()
channel_funnel['purchase_rate'] = channel_funnel['purchase_sessions']/channel_funnel['sessions']
channel_funnel = channel_funnel.sort_values(by='purchase_rate', ascending=False)
display(channel_funnel)
```
